column2: MAYBANK KIM ENG SECURITIES PTE LTD
UNITED OVERSEAS BANK NOMINEES PTE LTD
ON  THE  BASIS  OF  THE  INFORMATION  AVAILABLE  TO  THE  COMPANY,  APPROXIMATELY  33.08%  OF  THE  EQUITY  SECURITIES  OF  THE
COMPANY ARE HELD IN THE HANDS OF THE PUBLIC. THIS IS IN COMPLIANCE WITH RULE 723 OF THE LISTING MANUAL OF THE SGX-ST,
WHICH REQUIRES AT LEAST 10% OF A LISTED ISSUER’S EQUITY SECURITIES TO BE HELD BY THE PUBLIC.
